      <h2 id="why-hvac-coaching">Why HVAC Business Coaching Actually Works</h2>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>HVAC contractors who invest in quality coaching see an average ROI of 400-600% within the first year. This isn't because coaches wave magic wands, but because most contractors are making predictable mistakes that coaching systematically fixes.</p>

        <p>The most common issues we see cost contractors massive revenue:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Underpricing by 20-40%:</strong> Most contractors price based on what competitors charge rather than true cost plus desired margin</li>
          <li><strong>No systematic upselling:</strong> Average ticket increases 35-50% when contractors implement proper diagnostic and presentation systems</li>
          <li><strong>Poor technician productivity:</strong> Most techs complete 3-4 calls per day when 5-6 is achievable with better routing and systems</li>
          <li><strong>Ineffective marketing:</strong> Contractors waste $20,000-$50,000 annually on marketing that doesn't track or convert</li>
          <li><strong>Cash flow problems:</strong> Seasonal businesses need specific financial systems that most contractors lack</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Quality coaching addresses these systematically rather than hoping you'll figure it out through trial and error.</p>
      </div>

