        <p>Nexstar is the gold standard for HVAC business coaching, with over 600 member companies averaging $4.2M in annual revenue. Their approach combines monthly group coaching, quarterly workshops, peer networking, and extensive business systems.</p>

        <p><strong>What you get:</strong></p>
        <ul>
